modName: The Elder Scrolls V Expanded - Winterhold - Yorgrim Wall
summary: This is the fourth mod in The Elder Scrolls V: Expanded Series, Yorgrim Wall. This settlement is just south of Fort Kastav on the border between Winterhold and the Pale.
descriptionHtml:
This is the fourth mod in The Elder Scrolls V: Expanded Series, Yorgrim Wall. This settlement is just south of Fort Kastav on the border between Winterhold and the Pale. 

Can be considered Lore-Friendly however, there was never a settlement in Arena by that name. 

Compatibility: 

-Pretty Much Everything
author: RubikPanda
